  "duration": 119.913565312,
  "text": " The world is dominated by change and that means it's essential for you to react quickly and effectively in your market. However, is your IT robust and flexible enough to do this? And what steps should you take to create a modern ERP environment? These are often long and costly processes and have major impacts on your organization. You're making choices for the long term, but are they the right ones? We start with a scan to identify your goals, possible obstacles, and an intelligent ERP solution. It's also important to determine to what extent your organization is ready for the change. What follows is a recommendation on the roadmap and associated project approach. Always with the aim of making you resilient where you need to be and agile where you can be And always with value creation for your company and acceptance for your employees as a starting point our consultants will take you through the entire change process step by step we then implement and manage a modern and robust standard ERP system to make sure the core processes in your organization are in order all based on best practices The phased implementation process is clear and on budget yet pragmatic. Would a change in the work process, for example, not be more desirable? Or will we go for a fit-for-purpose solution after all? Customer experience and customer appreciation are central to everything we do. We have a committed and pragmatic approach and we're supported by our versatile ecosystem so that you are resilient where needed as well as agile and distinctive where you can be.",
